spx.sc.net

Interface HeartbeatID


  • public interface HeartbeatID
    Defines values for the heartbeat appId field. These values can be OR'ed together to indicate to listeners what services the sender can provide.

    For example, a server providing display functionality would use:
      SERVER | DISPLAY.

    A server providing scan-conversion functionality would use:
      SERVER | SCAN_CONV.

    The constants in this interface are kept in sync with the SPX_SCNET_HB_ID_... constants in "SPxScNet.h".
